
 Operating System :-
                     An operating system
                     (OS) is the core software that coordinates
                      everything happening on a computer. It sits between
                      the user, applications, and the system’s physical
                      hardware, acting as the invisible manager that
                      keeps the entire machine running as one unified system
                      It is translater between us and computer . It
                      help us to perform different task on computer
                      and it provide an interface through which we
                       can interact with computer .

